tags.name: Mono Pass
tags.note: This is where signs for Mono pass are on the terrain, west of Summit Lake. USGS topos and other maps put it east of the lake, at the boundary of Yosemite NP/Inyo NF. Keep it west of the lake unless there is a good reason to distrust real-world signage.
